Texts.Chs:
^orange;2级^reset;

对于一个有抱负的酒鬼来说，酿造是相当方便的技能。你现在可以浅尝一下酿酒工艺。不过还是要提醒你一下 - 这是个复杂的过程。你可以向科学前哨站的酿酒大师咨询一下。

^yellow;你知道吗？?^reset;早在2015年，Frackin’ Universe 就将 Starbooze mod 的啤酒酿造系统吞并进来了！^blue;译者直呼内行！^reset;

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 2^reset;

Brewing and winemaking are some pretty handy skills to know for an aspiring alcoholic. You can now dip your toes into the craft of booze-making. A word of warning, though - it's a complicated process. You may want to ask a master brewer at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset; for advice.

^yellow;Did you know?^reset; Frackin' Universe incorporated the beer-brewing system from the Starbooze mod way back in 2015!

Texts.Chs:
^orange;3级^reset;

你已经有了绘画的爱好。有了帆布作为你的...画布，你现在可以绘出漂亮的装饰艺术作品挂在你的实验室。

如果你钻研更多...^cyan;非凡^reset;的艺术追求，你会发现一个陌生的全新世界正等待着你。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 3^reset;

You've taken up the hobby of painting. With canvas as your... canvas, you can now create pretty decorative art pieces to hang around your lab.

If you delve into more...^cyan;unusual^reset; artistic pursuits, you'll find a whole new world of strangeness awaiting you.
